    <p>ScraperWiki&rsquo;s People Pack measurably increased my client&rsquo;s sales in a previously un-tapped market. Priceless.</p>
  </blockquote>
  <div class="person media">
    <img src="/image/avatar-rob.png" width="42" height="42" class="pull-left">
    <div class="media-body">
      <h4 class="media-heading">Rob Nightingale</h4>
      <p>Business Development Specialist</p>
